{"tid":2418484,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[翻案文] 如果4年前希拉蕊贏左川普，美國今日仲會唔會有武肺？","createTime":"2021-02-22T15:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T10:18:59.000Z","uid":52658,"like":19,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c6212ed17d3e35c01d99b0c78d990c1cbb006821","tid":2418484,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"美國疫情咁嚴重 點解要將d責任賴晒落川普度？<br />\n川普其實無做錯<br />\n當初川普話要封關果陣 <br />\n民主黨唔係跳晒出黎反對架咩？<br />\n川普只係衰在生不逢時 比美國人當做出氣袋<br />\n<br />\n我敢講民主黨一樣會做得咁差<br />\n如果當初希拉蕊上左既話 <br />\n世界真係唔知會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林肯係美國奠基者<br />\n雷根一手令美國成為霸主<br />\n咁川普就係一條支撐整個自由世界既支柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話川普係美國民族英雄都不為過<br />\n<br />\n一個疫情就抹殺左川普三年既政績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無諗過其實關川普乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係控制唔到d人唔帶口罩架wor<br />\n<br />\n反而係拜登你條契弟話會控制好翊晴架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜美國而家翊晴控制好喇咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母拜登<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8iXoKTJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8iXoKTJ.jpg&h=4cb542e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e30ad3403cc07db9ea69791d9581080ae3930a9f","tid":2418484,"uid":52658,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"川普唯一做錯既<br />\n就係任內無肅清你班聞屎黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e704a447f89347ecc10e37185a2c17c89c8dace6","tid":2418484,"uid":52658,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"希拉蕊感覺上比佢老公柯林頓更爛"},{"pid":"511216727d3d527b6dde97fb7ea6217c4a42490f","tid":2418484,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:17